{"tid":709432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國虐殺動物片買賣群組橫行！手段愈狠毒愈受歡迎","createTime":"2018-06-20T03:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T10:29:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6782724733c45057d63711211dd01c5ba88259e4","tid":709432,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"近年香港十分關注動物權益相關的議題，不少人都希望加強罰則。一來希望能加強保護小動物，二來警惕大家不要虐待動物。然而内地的情況就不同，除了依舊有每年一度的「狗肉節」，近日内地社交平台竟然出現了一些群組，公然買賣大量虐殺動物的影片，暫時亦似乎沒有法規杜絕問題！<br />\n<br />\n據内地媒體報道，在 QQ、帖吧等網絡社交媒體上，出現了一些分享、買賣虐殺動物影片的群組。據群組數據顯示，群内的成員大部份介乎 20 到 30 歲，6 成爲男性。成員們會分享各式各樣的虐待動物片段，由火燒、剝皮到割喉、上吊，施虐手法愈狠毒就愈受推崇，甚至被成員稱爲「大神」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2095000/2097313/animal02--_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2095000%2F2097313%2Fanimal02--_1024.jpg&h=1ded20ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而這些虐殺動物的片段價格十分便宜，一百部影片只需 ￥20（約為 HK$25），更是高清拍攝。成員甚至可以直接付錢加群，觀看虐待貓狗的直播片段，漸漸發展成另類賺錢的方法。雖然這些群組其後被指違反相關條例，被永久封停，然而換個帳號就能再次發佈，根本解決不了問題。<br />\n<br />\n可惜，現時内地法規只針對保護珍稀野生動物，「虐殺普通動物」的行爲暫時還不需要承擔法律責任，導致這些群組橫行，禁之不絕。内地愛護動物人士雖然不斷嘗試加群抗議、投訴，然而卻做不到更多，無奈之餘心痛。究竟什麽時候才能杜絕這些恐怖的群組呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2095000/2097313/animal3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2095000%2F2097313%2Fanimal3_600.jpg&h=ded23d04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2097313/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%99%90%E6%AE%BA%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E7%89%87%E8%B2%B7%E8%B3%A3%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84%E6%A9%AB%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%81%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E6%84%88%E7%8B%A0%E6%AF%92%E6%84%88%E5%8F%97%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2097313%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2599%2590%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%25B5%2584%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E8%25A1%258C%25EF%25BC%2581%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E6%2584%2588%25E7%258B%25A0%25E6%25AF%2592%25E6%2584%2588%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E&d=GMefUb1EwwwOqWogq8hO0zOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f2de2b4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2097313/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%99%90%E6%AE%BA%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E7%89%87%E8%B2%B7%E8%B3%A3%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84%E6%A9%AB%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%81%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E6%84%88%E7%8B%A0%E6%AF%92%E6%84%88%E5%8F%97%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69efa28b31ad573fa361903d98c43c0b243b0164","tid":709432,"uid":135767,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"468624fa11dee771169a12379b93973a170d397b","tid":709432,"uid":157362,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed1661c7104d498e76732a3d312899663d75be7a","tid":709432,"uid":139700,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"69efa28b31ad573fa361903d98c43c0b243b0164","tid":709432,"uid":135767,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:15:20.000Z","msg":"你又知當年批人都係咁？"},{"pid":"e42f59cb65b0c06fcf1107a57ebd3a340df221fc","tid":709432,"uid":139700,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"69efa28b31ad573fa361903d98c43c0b243b0164","tid":709432,"uid":135767,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:15:43.000Z","msg":"你又知當年批人都係咁？"},{"pid":"cb4c6d0e345af4942b1db8c85f0262102afab3f6","tid":709432,"uid":141200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"聽講殺人犯殺人之前好多都會虐殺動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry